{"tid":251510,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（真實經歷）交友App，微信叫雞陷阱","createTime":"2017-05-21T04:06:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-26T06:36:04.000Z","uid":98375,"like":1,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5a1ad30686e23543054bc25dfc9ae8da25220eeb","tid":251510,"uid":98375,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T04:06:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小弟毒拎一個，青頭一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n是咁的：我一時精蟲上腦，要叫雞破處，禁啱係交友App見到條女唔錯，佢叫我加佢wechat ，好啦我加左，約哂時間地點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到左之後再微信囡囡，佢話行緊黎，又問我電話，同埋話佢經理人會call搵我講規矩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係有個up普通話打黎講一大輪，用普通話交流，最後叫我唔好cut線＋唔用現金交收叫我去買點數卡⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我真係去左買唸都冇唸 （事後唸返好on9）買完同個經紀講，佢叫我收線然後用wechat影點數俾囡囡，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌點解我會照做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後，個經紀又打黎話怕我係警察放蛇，叫我影公司員工作証俾囡囡V7，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仆街我又真係影左，好在用美圖秀秀刪花哂先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後，經紀又打俾我講保釋囡囡要錢，要我交保証金$6600......又叫我用點數方式，又叫我唔洗驚，囡囡見面會俾返哂我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <strong>係呢刻</strong>，我開始覺得鬼鬼地.....我同佢講冇錢，佢開始恐嚇我響自己朵<del>雷豹</del>，果刻我真係<strong>心都震埋</strong>，話我係佢個埸玩野，會搵小弟黎搞我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咁吹我買$6600點數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我果時先開始冷靜返個人，金翅GG鳥，肯定係點數黨詐騙......我一句唔要果$800就收線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 事後，我不停收到+852頭嘅電話，我都唔聽，又収到囡囡wechat叫我小心啲惹到呢個大佬，我直接閪奔返屋企，當日又block哂果堆電話V7同WhatsApp 因為我真係好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 再夜啲仲收到SMS話佢會搞我屋企人廢左我......真係冇覺好訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <del></del>過左禁多日都仲好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n各位巴打想笑就笑啦，我唔介意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以後想破處直接去141啦，希望大家咪落V7搭，今次精蟲一時上腦，搞到我自己嘅理性都冇撚哂而中伏......<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ce2b7fa131a2c1333f30999eb277b3f2e92385f","tid":251510,"uid":76117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T04:09:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0f4ae4adcaa1901e23b4e9b67f42de1aa8f54d13","tid":251510,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T04:09:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af25b6f4d0586e7c9154721bc578df85ce5d90a5","tid":251510,"uid":78330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T04:09:59.000Z","msg":"咁張點數最後點"},{"pid":"6301ed2b9d306921a50d3acdfc76b0b43bb7848f","tid":251510,"uid":25014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T04:10:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔睇新聞"},{"pid":"ba843088ddb5122f90ea1fefcfe715b77d9a2868","tid":251510,"uid":9541,"like":0,